# BYON Secure Vault
# This directory stores encrypted sensitive data
# All contents except .gitkeep are gitignored
#
# Categories:
# - credentials/ : API keys, passwords, tokens
# - keys/        : SSH, GPG, crypto keys
# - financial/   : Banking, wallets, trading
# - documents/   : Legal, medical, personal
# - secrets/     : Generic secrets
#
# Security: All data encrypted with GPG or AES-256-GCM
